    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/06934368926009523143" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Patty</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2010/10/now-here-now-there/#comment-21183"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2010-10-16T12:05:44-04:00">Saturday, October 16, 2010 at 12:05 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
