      <p>What is odd is that I seem to be the only person who neither hates nor loves oysters. I will eat them, when offered, one or two or three, and they&#39;re okay. But not worth the money or trouble, to me. I&#39;m pretty open-minded and grew up eating shellfish of various kinds, sometimes really fresh from Long Island Sound.</p>
