    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I just can say that I can eat anything that comes from sea. Hope we can keep them clean so that we can enjoy even oysters:) </p>
<p>The only reason I had an oysterphobia for a while was that I got confused once and talked long and long about oyster eggs while I meant ostrich eggs! In my defense, English is my second language but my husband never let it go!</p>
