    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>@Ashley: Neti Pot, hahaaaaaaaaa! I love the taste of oysters, the &#8220;now here, now there,&#8221; can deal with small and fresh and a bit of chew (would not even dream of swallowing whole!), but as soon as I even THINK about the phlegmy, snotball, chewy, booger qualities they do indeed possess&#8211;and c&#39;mon, there&#39;s no denying that, folks&#8211;they almost make a return trip. So I wonder, why keep eating something I don&#39;t adore? Still, the taste keeps bringing me back, and I do eat them, perhaps 6 a year, just to keep an open mind.</p>
